    "name": "Ferrous Butterfly",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Ferrous Butterfly",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Beautiful but deadly, the ferrous butterfly is a turkey-sized insectile creature bristling with dozens of gleaming, razor-edged blades. Considered harmless by most denizens of the Plane of Metal, they nonetheless pose a significant threat to organic creatures, whose iron-rich blood they find irresistible.",
